      </div>

      <div class="feature-card highlight">
        <div class="feature-icon fi-orange">⚡</div>
        <h3>500k-Term Engine<span class="new-pill">NEW</span></h3>
        <p>HashSet word-tokenizer replaces regex alternation. O(text length) regardless of term count. 480,000-name lists run at the same speed as 100 terms. Greedy longest-match with Unicode and Hebrew support.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-card highlight">
        <div class="feature-icon fi-cyan">🔍</div>
        <h3>Live Tester &amp; Debug<span class="new-pill">NEW</span></h3>
