      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon fi-green">&#x1F3AF;</div>
        <h3>Configurable PII Fields</h3>
        <p>14 pre-seeded PII types (Israeli ID, DOB, phone, email, IBAN, passport, name&hellip;). Add custom Regex, keyword-list, context-aware, or LLM patterns per client. Inline chip editor for fast updates.</p>
